    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The engine struggles to start and requires significant mechanical attention, and the transmission exhibits frequent slipping. Visually, the body has extensive rust, several large dents, and the paint is peeling in multiple areas. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and most of the electronic features, including the radio and air conditioning, are currently non-functional. This car is best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a major project or parts vehicle.",
